Some polishing of code

Split out FetcherPlacesAPI from RemoteAPIFetchers. That library is purely about fetching and parsing results. GeneralLibrary and Reviewer have copies of the old FetcherPlacesAPI (GooglePlacesApi and PlacesApi respectively) to extract primitives etc. as they see fit.
Some adjustments for changing to PlacesApi
Changed location dialog to show distances to autocomplete suggestions

Changed location dialog and removed distances to autocomplete suggestions. Too slow and too much data usage. When autocomplete selected, fetches location then for selection only.

Added LayoutLocationEdit for a simple dialog for editing location name. Long click on location grid item no asks if you want to be taken to the map screen. Long click on banner button takes you to map screen.
Test for AddLocation dialog
Test for EditLocation dialog
